lms were also awarded a total of three [[Special Achievement Academy Award|Special Achievement Awards]]. ''The Empire Strikes Back'' and ''Return of the Jedi'' received Special Achievement Awards for their visual effects,<ref name=\"Oscars1981\" /><ref name=\"Oscars1984\" /> and ''Star Wars'' received a Special Achievement Award for its alien, creature and robot voices.<ref name=\"Oscars1978\" /><ref name=\"BurttOscar\">{{cite news|url=http://aaspeechesdb.oscars.org/link/050-23/ |title=To Benjamin Burtt, Jr. for the creation of the alien, creature and robot voices featured in \"Star Wars.\" |accessdate=December 23, 2017 |publisher=[[Academy Awards]] Acceptance Speech |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171223200116/http://aaspeechesdb.oscars.org/link/050-23/ |archivedate=December 23, 2017 }}</ref>\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center;\" width=99%;\n! align=\"center\" width=\"16%\" | {{small|Film}}\n! align=\"center\" width=\"6.66%\" | {{small|[[Academy Award for Best Picture|Best Picture]]}}\n! align=\"center\" width=\"6.66%\" | {{small|[[Academy Award for Best Director|Best Director]]}}\n! align=\"center\" width=\"6.66%\" | {{small|[[Academy Award for Best Supporting Actor|Best Supporting Actor]]}}\n! align=\"center\" width=\"6.66%\" | {{small|[[Academy Award for Best Original Screenplay|Best Original Screenplay]]}}\n! align=\"center\" width=\"6.66%\" | {{small|[[Academy Award for Best Costume Design|Best Costume Design]]}}\n! align=\"center\" width=\"6.66%\" | {{small|[[Academy Award for Best Film Editing|Best Film Editing]]}}\n! align=\"center\" width=\"6.66%\" | {{small|[[Academy Award for Best Makeup and Hairstyling|Best Makeup]]}}\n! align=\"center\" width=\"6.66%\" | {{small|[[Academy Award for Best Original Score|Best Original Score]]}}\n! align=\"center\" width=\"6.66%\" | {{small|[[Academy Award for Best Production Design|Best Production Design]]}}\n! align=\"center\" width=\"6.66%\" | {{small|[[Academy Award for Best Sound Editing|Best Sound Editing]]}}\n! align=\"center\" width=\"6.66%\" | {{small|[[Academy Award for Best Sound Mixing|Best Sound Mixing]]}}\n! align=\"center\" width=\"6.66%\" | {{small|[[Academy Award for Best Visual Effects|Best Visual Effects]]}}\n! scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\"| {{Abbr|Ref.|Reference}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''A New Hope''\n| colspan=\"2\" {{nom}}\n| {{nom}}{{efn|group=lower-roman|[[Alec Guinness]] for his performance as [[Obi-Wan Kenobi]].}}\n| {{nom}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{won}}\n| style=\"background-color:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n| colspan=\"2\" {{won}}\n| style=\"background-color:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n| rowspan=\"2\" {{won}}\n| {{won}}\n| style=\"text-align:center\" |<ref name=\"Oscars1978\">{{cite news|url=http://www.oscars.org/oscars/ceremonies/1978 |title=The 50th Academy Awards (1978) Nominees and Winners |accessdate=December 22, 2017 |publisher=[[Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences]] (AMPAS) |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171222075847/http://www.oscars.org/oscars/ceremonies/1978 |archivedate=December 22, 2017 }}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''The Empire Strikes Back''\n| style=\"background-color:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n| style=\"background-color:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n| style=\"background-color:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n| style=\"background-color:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n| style=\"background-color:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n| style=\"background-color:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n| style=\"background-color:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n| rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\" {{nom}}\n| style=\"background-color:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n| rowspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color:greenyellow;\" | Special Achievement\n| style=\"text-align:center\" |<ref name=\"Oscars1981\">{{cite news|url=http://www.oscars.org/oscars/ceremonies/1981 |title=The 53rd Academy Awards (1981) Nominees and Winners |accessdate=December 22, 2017 |publisher=[[Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences]] (AMPAS) |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/we